column3: The awarded loans will settle on December 17, 2009, and will mature on January 14, 2010. The stop-out rate shown above will apply to all awarded loans.
column4: Institutions that submitted winning bids will be contacted by their respective Reserve Banks by 11:30 a.m. EST on December 15, 2009. Participants have until 12:30 p.m. EST on December 15, 2009, to inform their local Reserve Bank of any error.
